---
// Our Approach section for CRE industry page
---

<section id="approach" class="cre-approach-section">
  <div class="cre-approach-container">
    <span class="section-label">OUR APPROACH FOR CRE</span>
    <h2 class="cre-approach-headline">
      Purpose-built systems for deal velocity
    </h2>
    <p class="cre-approach-intro">
      We don't build generic software and force it into your workflow. We architect systems specifically for how CRE firms operate—from deal sourcing through portfolio management. Every feature is designed to eliminate friction and accelerate decision-making.
    </p>

    <div class="cre-approach-grid">
      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Deal velocity infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We build unified platforms that connect your entire deal pipeline—from sourcing through closing. Every system is designed to reduce time-to-decision, not just store data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Intelligent automation</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We embed AI and automation into your core workflows—automating underwriting calculations, generating investor reports, and surfacing market intelligence—so your team focuses on judgment, not data entry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Ownership and control</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          You own the systems we build. No vendor lock-in, no subscription dependencies. We architect for long-term ownership, giving you the flexibility to evolve as your firm grows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-approach-section {
    background: #000000;
    padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cre-approach-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .cre-approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .cre-approach-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 32px;
    background: transparent;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-approach-card:hover {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .cre-approach-card:hover .cre-approach-card-title {
    color: #000000;
  }

  .cre-approach-card:hover .cre-approach-card-description {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-approach-card-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-approach-card-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-approach-section {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }

    .cre-approach-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

